side, the action.

00:02:25.920 --> 00:02:28.650
So it's pretty clearly split
between the two sides.

00:02:28.650 --> 00:02:31.270
I think that it's a very
important to follow, this

00:02:31.270 --> 00:02:31.970
general layout.

00:02:31.970 --> 00:02:35.740
If you do decide to deviate in
some way, shape, or form, you

00:02:35.740 --> 00:02:37.220
should just always keep
this in mind.

00:02:37.220 --> 00:02:39.310
And try and stick to this
if you possibly can.

00:02:39.310 --> 00:02:41.750
