Really awesome tool.

00:26:02.750 --> 00:26:04.830
We use it in a lot
of our samples.

00:26:08.070 --> 00:26:09.870
ADAM: There's an additional
style, called action bar

00:26:09.870 --> 00:26:13.310
overlay style that you can use
if, say the content is just so

00:26:13.310 --> 00:26:16.070
important in this particular
screen, you can really make

00:26:16.070 --> 00:26:18.220
the action bar and system
Chrome fade out

00:26:18.220 --> 00:26:19.430
a little bit here.

00:26:19.430 --> 00:26:20.820
So there's two examples here.

00:26:20.820 --> 00:26:23.410
One is Google Maps, on
the right there.

00:26:23.410 --> 00:26:25.640
And you can see the map is,
obviously, just the most

00:26:25.640 --> 00:26:28.140
important thing within an
application like Google Maps.

00:26:28.140 --> 00:26:30.240
And so you can see it's
transparent, allowing the map

00:26:30.240 --> 00:26:32.150
to bleed through a
little bit there.

00:26:32.150 --> 00:26:33.780
It looks really, really nice.

00:26:33.780 --> 00:26:37.840
And then the system gallery is
another great example, which

00:26:37.840 --> 00:26:39.520
we're using right now.

00:26:39.520 --> 00:26:43.760
And one thing you should do is
if, something like gallery,

00:26:43.760 --> 00:26:45.970
where you the user may want to
see the picture without any

00:26:45.970 --> 00:26:49.600
other Chrome visible, touching
the screen should really make

00:26:49.600 --> 00:26:52.540
the actual bar come on screen,
then disappear again--

00:26:52.540 --> 00:26:54.260
ROMAN: Along with
the status bar.

00:26:54.260 --> 00:26:56.210
ADAM: And potentially the status
bar as well, and the

00:26:56.210 --> 00:26:57.470
system controls on the bottom.

00:26:57.470 --> 00:26:58.770
That's not really possible with

00:26:58.770 --> 00:26:59.950
something like photo viewing.

00:26:59.950 --> 00:27:02.780
But with video viewing, you can
actually make the entire

00:27:02.780 --> 00:27:04.450
thing go full screen.

00:27:04.450 --> 00:27:07.200
ROMAN: And for developers out
there, there's a template that

00:27:07.200 --> 00:27:08.830
