ADAM: Custom action views,
Nick, do you want to--?

00:27:20.200 --> 00:27:20.520
Very quick.

00:27:20.520 --> 00:27:21.695
NICK: Yeah, sure.

00:27:21.695 --> 00:27:22.446
ADAM: You've got five words.

00:27:22.446 --> 00:27:24.920
NICK: [INAUDIBLE] don't just
