00:27:30.180 --> 00:27:33.950
So you have a common pattern is
to transform a refresh icon

00:27:33.950 --> 00:27:36.620
into an indeterminate
progress spinner.

00:27:36.620 --> 00:27:39.680
So you can use the same space
