00:28:18.770 --> 00:28:19.680
So it's easy.

00:28:19.680 --> 00:28:21.780
So you have this richer behavior
from the action

00:28:21.780 --> 00:28:24.310
buttons, not just
simple buttons.

00:28:24.310 --> 00:28:26.220
ADAM: Cool, excellent.

00:28:26.220 --> 00:28:28.440
And I think Nick was talking
